data.description: Welcome Home!!! Located in the highly desirable Hempfield school district's Jacobs Creek neighborhood 2390 Spring Valley road is one of the most central and convenient locations Lancaster has to offer. Just minutes from 30, 283, shopping, restaurants, bars & all downtown Lancaster has to offer. This home boasts over 2500 sqft of finished spaced between 5 beds 3.5 baths and a finished basement. You'll love the layout featuring a spacious kitchen with breakfast nook, formal dining room, office, living with with a gas fireplace, wonderful primary suite with big walk-in closet and en-suite bath, 3 additional 2nd floor bedrooms,  Home could use a little cosmetic TLC but is priced accordingly. Showings begin Sunday 4/21 at 1pm until 4pm at the open house.
